{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_LIN_020.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1e,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Linca, you're amazing...<CR>To be able to swing a sword around like that, even though you're a girl..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hm? Is what I am doing that amazing?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "It sure is! If it was me, I wouldn't even be able to lift it up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I am confident in my abilities with a sword. I could do this before enjoying a balanced breakfast."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Although, in reality, my combat abilities increase after I reap the benefits of my morning meal."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yet, even before a meal, I will not be defeated by a wild beast..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Y-Yeah, I get what you're saying about the meals. I guess you went through a lot of training..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Yes. I cannot remember how many times I have swung my sword."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xa,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "In the beginning, it was I who<CR>was being swung by the sword,<CR>but now, I can even do this."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Wow wow wow, that's amazing!<CR>You're so cool!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Your excitement from me just swinging my sword...has surprised me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Every time you swing it, your hair flows...like a mythical goddess!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "My hair... It would be easier to fight if it was shorter or if I just did not have any..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "But Marion will not allow me to cut it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "And as it grew out, she started saying absurd things, like to comb it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I see... I-Is that absurd...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I believe that the shorter your hair is, the less it will get in your way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "That's absolutely not true! Your hair style right now is absolutely lovely!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "You can't cut it, Linca!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... Ayesha, you are starting to talk like Marion..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "That's cuz Marion's correct. Linca,<CR>you look very lovely right now!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Hmhm. Either way, Marion is like your mentor."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x168,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Certainly. For example, do not pick food up off the ground and eat it, or do not follow strangers..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x16a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "She frequently scolds me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x16b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I have only done each one once so far."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Oh, so you have done that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Do not worry. Those instances happened a while ago."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x9,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Between you and me, if a band of<CR>criminals came to take me away today,<CR>I am sure I could return on my own."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Th-That's reassuring...I think..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Yes, it is reassuring.<CR>Now, we should go."
        }
    ]
}